<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Suspension Notification</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f7f6;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      .headline {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        background-color: #e74c3c;
        padding: 20px;
        padding-top: 40px;
        padding-bottom: 40px;
        color: white;
        text-align: left;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        max-width: 600px;
        text-align: left; /* Align text to the left */
        background-color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px; /* Increased padding to the left and right */
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .text {
        font-size: 0.9rem; /* Reduced font size */
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .importantText {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #e74c3c;
      }
      .signature {
        font-size: 0.8rem; /* Reduced font size */
        color: #555;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .importantText {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #5b83f1;
      }
      .linkText {
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #3c6cf1;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="headline">
        Your Shuttle Bus System Account Has Been Suspended.
      </h1>
     <div style="padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
      <p class="text">
        Hi, <span class="importantText"><%=username%></span>
      </p>
      <p class="text">
        We hope this message finds you well. We regret to inform you that your account on the Shuttle Bus System has been temporarily suspended as of now, in accordance with the terms and conditions of KIT.
      </p>
      <p class="text">
        If you think that this suspension is a mistake or if there are extenuating circumstances, we encourage you to reach out to our team at <a href="mailto:<%=sbsTeam%>" class="linkText">email</a> as soon as possible. Our dedicated support team is ready to assist you.
      </p>
      <p class="text">
        You will not be able to use the system unless successfully appealed.
      </p>
      <p class="signature">Best regards,<br />The Shuttle Bus System Team</p>
     </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
